title: The Giants Of Thessaly (1960)
description:
1960
Action, Adventure
87 Mins

In order to placate the angry gods, who have allowed Thessaly to be overrun with barbarian invaders and beset with natural disasters, King Jason takes his Argonauts on a search for the fabled Golden Fleece.





Director: Riccardo Freda

Writers: Giuseppe Masini (screenplay), Mario Rossetti (screenplay)

Stars: Roland Carey, Ziva Rodann, Alberto Farnese
